'''Lot lizard''' is a [[prostitute]] at a truck stop. It is one of the lower rungs of the [[sex industry]] heirarchy. The term was popularized by the book [[Sarah (novel)|Sarah]] which is a fictional account of the life of a truck stop prostitute.

==External link==
[http://www.myspace.com/lotlizardmusic Lot Lizard] is also the name of a metal band from Marshall County, Alabama.

